---
title: Almond Chicken Escalopes with Sweet Potato Mash and Broccoli
description: A crunchy, golden outer coating of almonds, parsley and mustard makes these chicken escalopes the perfect midweek meal to look forward to. Keeping things simple, we’ve served the chicken alongside sweet potato mash and roasted broccoli for extra veg goodness.
